 X \langle Y, Z\rangle = \tilde X \langle \tilde Y ,\tilde Z\rangle = \langle \nabla^M_{\tilde X} \tilde Y, \tilde Z\rangle + \langle \tilde Y, \nabla^M_{\tilde X} \tilde Z\rangle = \langle  \nabla_{\tilde X}^M \tilde Y, Z\rangle + \langle Y, \nabla_{\tilde X}^M \tilde Z\rangle
 = \langle  p(\nabla_{\tilde X}^M \tilde Y), Z\rangle + \langle Y, p(\nabla_{\tilde X}^M \tilde Z)\rangle = \langle \nabla^N_{X} Y, Z \rangle + \langle Y, \nabla_X^N Z\rangle.
